WEBVTT

1
00:49:35.960 --> 00:49:37.440 
你有电话吗？
Do you have a phone?

2
00:49:37.480 --> 00:49:39.480 
没有，我拆掉了
No, I had it pulled.

3
00:49:39.480 --> 00:49:41.480 
因为太多人打电话来
'Cause people calling all the time...

4
00:49:41.480 --> 00:49:44.280 
我是说谁想被人打扰
and who needs the aggravation, right?

5
00:49:44.280 --> 00:49:45.560 
对吧？
Interruptions?

6
00:49:45.560 --> 00:49:47.160 
你想打给谁？
Who'd you wanna call?

7
00:49:47.200 --> 00:49:49.920 
我哥哥，告诉他我在哪里
I wanna let my brother know where I am.

8
00:49:51.160 --> 00:49:52.280 
为什么？
Why?

9
00:49:53.800 --> 00:49:55.640 
我怕他会担心
I think he might be worried.

10
00:49:55.640 --> 00:49:58.680 
我打给他，如果你担心的话
I'll call your brother, if that's the problem.

